Package org.cibseven.bpm.engine.impl.bpmn.parser

Class BpmnParse

java.lang.Object
org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
org.cibseven.bpm.engine.impl.util.xml.Parse
org.cibseven.bpm.engine.impl.bpmn.parser.BpmnParse
All Implemented Interfaces:
ContentHandler, DTDHandler, EntityResolver, ErrorHandler
public class BpmnParse extends Parse
Specific parsing of one BPMN 2.0 XML file, created by the BpmnParser. Instances of this class should not be reused and are also not threadsafe.
Author:
